#: ../../cxflow/architecture.md:72
msgid ""
"**Markdown SSOT** — `md_source` stores raw Markdown; `html_cache` is "
"computed on-the-fly"
msgstr ""
"**Markdown SSOT** — `md_source`에 원본 Markdown 저장; `html_cache`는 "
"실시간으로 계산"

#: ../../cxflow/architecture.md:73
msgid ""
"**Optimistic Locking** — `version` counter prevents concurrent edit "
"conflicts"
msgstr ""
"**낙관적 잠금** — `version` 카운터로 동시 편집 충돌 방지"

#: ../../cxflow/architecture.md:74
msgid ""
"**Workflow State Machine** — configurable transition policy with "
"group/author checks"
msgstr ""
"**워크플로우 상태 머신** — 그룹/작성자 검사를 포함한 설정 가능한 전환 정책"

#: ../../cxflow/architecture.md:75
